       <table border="0" width="100%">             
 <tr>             
  <td width="100%">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;      
             
  <p class="MsoNormal" align="center" style="text-align:center"><span style="font-size:22.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;font-family:方正隶书简体;
mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;">武汉大学简况</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:22.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:方正隶书简体"><o:p>
</o:p>
</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent:22.0pt"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;
mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;
mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;">武汉大学创建于</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt">1893</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:
&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;">年，是中华人民共和国教育部直属的重点综合性大学，位于风景秀丽的武汉市东湖之滨、珞珈山麓。恰逢世纪之交，武汉大学迎来了新的发展机遇。今年，武汉大学、武汉水利电力大学、武汉测绘科技大学和湖北医科大学组建了新的武汉大学。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt"><o:p>
</o:p>
</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent:22.0pt"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;
mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;
mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;">新组建的武汉大学有本科专业</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt">117</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:
&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;">个，硕士学位授权专业</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt">185</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:
&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;">个，博士学位授权专业</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt">77</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:
&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;">个，有博士后科研流动站</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt">11</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:
&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;">个，国家级重点学科</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt">11</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:
&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;">个，</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt">7</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:
&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;">个学科专业被确定为国家基础科学人才培养基地，国家重点实验室和国家专业实验室</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt">7</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:
&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;">个，国家工程中心</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt">2</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:
&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;">个。学校现有教师</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt">4000</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:
&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;">多人，其中中国科学院院士</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt">5</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:
&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;">人，中国工程院院士</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt">5</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:
&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;">人，欧亚科学院院士</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt">2</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:
&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;">人，博士生导师</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt">348</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:
&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;">人，教授</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt">1058</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:
&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;">人，副教授</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt">2075</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:
&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;">人。在校学生</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt">4</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:
&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;">万余人，其中博士硕士研究生</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt">6460</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:
&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;">人，各类留学生</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt">455</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:
&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;">人。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt"><o:p>
</o:p>
</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent:22.0pt"><span style="font-size:12.0pt;
mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;
mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;">武汉大学留学生教育学院是负责全校各类留学生的招生、管理、汉语培训、汉语言文学专业教学的专门机构。学院为全国</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt">HSK</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:
&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;">和对外汉语教师资格考试的考点之一。留学生教育学院现有专职对外汉语教师</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt">25</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:
&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;">人，其中教授</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt">2</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:
&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;">人，副教授</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt">13</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:
&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;">人，博士</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt">3</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:
&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;">人，硕士</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt">5</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:
&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;">人，世界汉语教学学会会员</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt">4</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:
&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;">人，中国对外汉语教学学会会员</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt">20</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:
&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;">人，</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt">18</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:
&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;">人获对外汉语教师资格证书，</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt">12</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:
&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;">人有出国任教经历。另外我校还聘请了</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt">20</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:
&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;">名兼职教师，其中博士生导师</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt">3</span><span style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:
&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;">名。</span><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:10.0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:
黑体"><o:p>
</o:p>
</span></p>

                    
